# hotkeys
g - move current selected object.
gz, gz, gx - move in a specific axis
g(middle click) - move with snapping to axis closest to mouse
similar for s (scale), and and r (rotate).


touchpad you can emulate 3 button mouse (edit... preferences)

ctrl is incremental changes

## movement
- orbit middle click move
- shift middle click pan
- ctrl middle click zoom
- numpad . or \` focus on object


- view from camera


